<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Arepas con Queso | Taste The Movies</title>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Taste The Movies</h1>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section>
      <div>
        <img src="images/placeholder.png" alt="Arepas con Queso from Encanto" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Colombian Cheese-Stuffed Arepas</h2>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong></p>
        <p>Mirabel’s mom heals with these—emotionally and literally! A comforting and delicious dish from *Encanto*.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div>
        <h3>Ingredients</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>2 cups masarepa (precooked cornmeal, like PAN)</li>
          <li>1½ cups warm water</li>
          <li>1 cup shredded mozzarella or queso blanco</li>
          <li>Salt</li>
          <li>Butter or oil for frying</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3>Instructions</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Mix the masarepa, warm water, and salt to form dough. Let it rest for 5 minutes.</li>
          <li>Shape the dough into patties and stuff each with cheese inside.</li>
          <li>Cook the patties on a greased skillet for 5-7 minutes per side until golden and the cheese is melty inside.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
